OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FThe downturn in housing market
OL,7,Factivity may potentially be starting
OL,8,Fto stabilise, according to surveyors.
OL,10,FA net balance of 34% of property
OL,11,Fprofessionals reported in May that new
OL,12,Fbuyer inquiries were falling rather
OL,13,Fthan rising, the Royal Institution of
OL,14,FChartered Surveyors (Rics) said.
OL,16,FWhile this continued to point to
OL,17,Fweaker housing market demand, it was
OL,18,Fthe first time since January that
OL,19,Fdemand had not moved further into
OL,20,Fnegative territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
