FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781139789
OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FThe fall in agreed sales was also
OL,7,Funchanged in May, with a net balance
OL,8,Fof 37% of professionals seeing sales
OL,9,Ffall.
OL,11,FThe unchanged reading suggests the
OL,12,Fpace of decline is no longer
OL,13,Fintensifying, Rics said.
OL,15,FBut it also said that sales are taking
OL,16,Flonger to complete, with the average
OL,17,Ftime from listing to completion
OL,18,Fsitting at 21.5 weeks ` the longest
OL,19,Ftime since Rics started recording
OL,20,Fthese particular figures in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781139789
OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FHouse prices are also falling overall,
OL,7,Fwith a net balance of 35% of
OL,8,Fprofessionals seeing falls.
OL,10,FProfessionals in the South East and
OL,11,FEast Anglia reported more pronounced
OL,12,Fdownward pressure on prices, while
OL,13,Fthose in Northern Ireland continued to
OL,14,Fsee firm price growth, Rics said.
OL,16,FLooking to 12 months' time, a small
OL,17,Fbalance of 2% of professionals expect
OL,18,Fto see sales pick up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781139789
OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FAnd while house prices are also
OL,7,Fexpected to fall overall in the next
OL,8,Fthree months, a balance of 6% of
OL,9,Fsurveyors expect prices to be higher
OL,10,Fin the year ahead.
OL,12,FMortgage rates jumped amid economic
OL,13,Funcertainty prompted by the conflict
OL,14,Fin the Middle East, but in recent
OL,15,Fweeks some lenders have been cutting
OL,16,Frates.
OL,18,FRics said the rental market also
OL,19,Fremains under pressure, with rising
OL,20,Fdemand from tenants and falling
OL,21,Flandlord instructions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
