OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781139789
OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FTarrant Parsons, Rics head of market
OL,7,Fresearch and analysis, said: "The
OL,8,Flatest survey data suggest the recent
OL,9,Fdownturn in activity may be beginning
OL,10,Fto stabilise, with several key
OL,11,Findicators broadly holding steady.
OL,13,F"However, as they remain in negative
OL,14,Fterritory, it would be premature to
OL,15,Finterpret this as the start of a
OL,16,Frecovery."
