OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FThe report was released as separate
OL,7,Fresearch from Zoopla indicated that UK
OL,8,Frents for new lets increased by 2.1%
OL,9,Fin the 12 months to April, falling
OL,10,Ffrom 2.6% a year ago.
OL,12,FZoopla also said that in areas where
OL,13,Faverage rents are #750 per month or
OL,14,Fless, rents are typically rising by 5%
OL,15,Fon average ` over twice the national
OL,16,Faverage of 2.1%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
