OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781139789
OL,3,CSubdued housing market may be starting
OL,4,Cto stabilise ` surveyors
OL,6,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,7,FZoopla, said: "Rent inflation is more
OL,8,Fsubdued across most of the UK's major
OL,9,Fcities due to already stretched
OL,10,Faffordability levels for renters."
